Package ch.unibas.bsc.detapp.level

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LevelType
    Empty interface to create a common parent for LevelElementType and LevelBuildingBlock.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Level
    Class which holds list of type LevelElement describing the level and the map update time.
    LevelBuilder
    For a given path to a json file this class handles the correct creation of a Level object.
    LevelBuildingBlock
    Class to store the name of a BuildBlock file.
    LevelElement
    Represents a level element by storing each GameObjectTypes per lane.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    LevelElementType
    Enum which stores the different available element types that can be used in a level json representation.
